==== 評價 ====
[[IGN|IGN]]的A·E·史派羅稱讚道：「佐原瑞的漫畫讓動畫中讓人摸不著頭腦的橋段變得清楚。」<ref name="Sparrow"/>[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的塞隆·馬汀（Theron Martin）認為漫畫版有著「承載著動人情感的強烈故事，充實了原版的動畫」，但「對結局的補充沒有必要」，且「角色設計不是新海誠的長處，佐原瑞也只有做到稍微加強而已」<ref>{{cite web|last=Martin|first=Theron|date=2006-08-24|title=The Voices of a Distant Star G.novel|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/voices-of-a-distant-star/manga|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=2010-11-11|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210091719/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/voices-of-a-distant-star/manga|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Comic Worth Reading的約翰納·德雷珀·卡爾森評論道：「漫畫版的作畫密度比許多日本漫畫都來得高，別具風格的背景支撐著筆下的世界。角色的臉孔時常隱沒在陰影中，暗示著分離和失去。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Carlson|first=Johanna Draper|date=2007-09-19|title=The Voices of A Distant Star – Best of 2006|url=http://comicsworthreading.com/2007/09/19/the-voices-of-a-distant-star-best-of-2006/|publisher=Comic Worth Reading|access-date=2010-11-11|language=en|archive-date=2012-01-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64wE2ClU3?url=http://comicsworthreading.com/2007/09/19/the-voices-of-a-distant-star-best-of-2006/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Pop Culture Shock的梅琳達·比西（Melinda Beasi）則寫道：「漫畫版的美可說是絕對的。畫功相當精緻且富表現力，而版面配置，像是對話和旁白文字的位置和風格，讓故事在視覺上更具吸引力，也很容易跟得上內容。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Beasi|first=Melinda|date=2008-12-12|title=''The Voices of a Distant Star''|url=http://www.popcultureshock.com/manga/index.php/manga-recon/the-voices-of-a-distant-star/|publisher=Pop Culture Shock|access-date=2010-11-11|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110624061527/http://www.popcultureshock.com/manga/index.php/manga-recon/the-voices-of-a-distant-star/|archive-date=2011-06-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>Mania.com的薩庫拉·伊瑞斯（Sakura Eries）批評漫畫「背景的細節不足，機甲設計乏味，動畫中令人嘆為觀止的場面在漫畫版中也被改得很沒衝擊力」<ref name="Eries">{{cite web|last=Eries|first=Sakura|date=2006-10-13|title=''Voices of a Distant Star'' Vol. #01|url=http://www.mania.com/voices-distant-star-vol-01_article_83146.html|publisher=Mania.com|access-date=2013-12-16|language=en|archive-url=https://archive.today/20131216065112/http://www.mania.com/voices-distant-star-vol-01_article_83146.html|archive-date=2013-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

